page.title: 11PRIVATE HOUSING
page.content: Danesholme estate has private housing in{six}of its streets.The houses are all made from{different coloured {brick}(unlike the council houses). Some of these houses have double garages,and some of their gardens are quite big.All of the private houses have{front}and{back}gardens,most of which are well cared for. The private houses look a lot flashier than the council houses on the outside. The private houses on the estate tend to be around the edges of the estate near the countryside or Kingswood. A lot of the people who own private houses on Danesholme lived in other parts of Corby before they moved to Danesholme.
